casebody.data:
Isabel Del Pino ALLEN, Appellant(s)/Petitioner(s),
v.
UNITED FACULTY OF MIAMI DADE COLLEGE FEA, AFL-CIO, AFT LOCAL 4253, Appellee(s)/Respondent(s), CASE NO.: 3D18-1073 District Court of Appeal of Florida, Third District. JULY 19, 2018 LAGOA, FERNANDEZ and LUCK, JJ., concur.

Following review of the petition for writ of prohibition, and the response and reply thereto, it is ordered that said petition is hereby denied.
